Lianne Hindle suffered a cardiac arrest at North Manchester General Hospital in December . 
  Her partner Chris Barnes is calling for action to prevent further tragedies at the scandal-hit hospital . 
  Three babies and one mother died at the hospital between December 2013 and July last year . 
  Ms Hindle gave birth to daughter Poppy in December but died three hours later . 
  The 37-year-old was left alone with a student midwife after the birth . 
  Her death came just months after the deaths of four babies and two mothers at the Royal Oldham Hospital . 
 